Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.04,0:00:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,润
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.90,0:00:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.77,0:00:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.31,0:00:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.24,0:00:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不需要自责
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.50,0:00:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说到底只是个人类吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.12,0:00:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.00,0:00:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.80,0:01:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来我猜对了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.49,0:02:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开始拍了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.02,0:02:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女主角得知恋人死去时的场景 第五次开拍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.38,0:02:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要走一周？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.87,0:02:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首领离开这么久不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.99,0:02:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有些事情非得我亲自去谈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.22,0:02:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖享受学校生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.88,0:03:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 好 我可一直都是好孩子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.63,0:03:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你骗人 我不信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.06,0:03:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停 停！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.43,0:03:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,集最近好像跟以前不太一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.19,0:03:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,变得自信满满了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.56,0:03:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟换了个人似的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.48,0:03:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说不定是在大岛发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.40,0:03:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,南方小岛的假日 一整个夏天的男女恋爱冒险
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.03,0:03:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后少年就变成了成人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.20,0:03:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.41,0:03:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但真是这样 人生不如意十之八九啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.38,0:03:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还在想谷寻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.50,0:03:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去设施那问了 都说没再见过他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.26,0:03:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前经常在一起玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.22,0:03:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要找的东西在水族馆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.35,0:03:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要找的又不是鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.52,0:03:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.06,0:03:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.31,0:03:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱的幸运物是虎皮条纹的水壶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.40,0:03:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到哪去找那种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.57,0:04:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个是？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.37,0:04:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虎皮条纹的水壶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.49,0:04:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.70,0:04:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.16,0:04:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,集？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.46,0:04:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 你俩还没回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.75,0:04:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是樱满你的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.05,0:04:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飒太拍片子用的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.46,0:04:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恋人的遗物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.13,0:04:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说是要让祈拿着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.31,0:04:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有东西落在社团教室了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.35,0:04:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个我替你带过去 你就陪祭去购物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.48,0:04:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.44,0:04:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花音…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.24,0:04:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幸运的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.15,0:04:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.45,0:04:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油~ 加油~ 幸运的机会~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.83,0:04:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么幸运的机会？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.95,0:04:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.46,0:04:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听说幽灵出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.55,0:05:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人用樱满黑周的身份进入大岛的研究所
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.43,0:05:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么想解释的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.56,0:05:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黒巣博士曾经的同事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.35,0:05:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,茎道修一郎博士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.52,0:05:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.37,0:05:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,购物在哪下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.50,0:05:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要买很多吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.54,0:05:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.34,0:05:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我拿得动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.59,0:05:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.27,0:05:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.65,0:05:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.48,0:06:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,集 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.15,0:06:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…对你…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.96,0:06:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.38,0:06:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谷寻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.06,0:06:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,集
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.97,0:06:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 玩得高兴？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.06,0:06:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想错了 谷寻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.60,0:06:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.15,0:06:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谷寻 别的没什么要说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.78,0:06:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想让我说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.94,0:06:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这里把一切和盘托出？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.41,0:06:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祭 你自己去购物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.33,0:06:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.83,0:06:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想跟谷寻谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.46,0:07:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,樱满集同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.84,0:07:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直盯着你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.93,0:07:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是明智之举
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.43,0:07:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们说要把润处理掉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.77,0:07:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们趁乱逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.86,0:07:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能让润继续待在那
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.08,0:07:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,取笑我吧 这是背叛你才做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.91,0:07:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总算逃出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.22,0:07:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,润
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.26,0:07:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又摔下来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.35,0:07:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪里疼吗 润
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.81,0:07:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 润
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.44,0:08:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是哥哥的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.27,0:08:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.95,0:08:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经锁定逃跑中的患者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.37,0:08:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好 干劲不错！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.37,0:08:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抓个患者而已 有必要出动我的End Rave吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.66,0:08:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你错了 男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.50,0:08:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龙打史莱姆时也不放水的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.30,0:08:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龙根本不吃史莱姆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.55,0:08:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以 伤疤脸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.01,0:08:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK 丹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.43,0:08:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.10,0:08:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会用干劲来完成任务的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.27,0:08:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,处世之道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.49,0:08:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能借我点钱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.78,0:08:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逃亡和吃饭都需要钱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.16,0:09:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特地让我看润就是为了这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.25,0:09:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求求你了 集
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.50,0:09:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在只有我才能保护润
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.59,0:09:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.73,0:09:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,集？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.27,0:09:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,涯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.31,0:09:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.73,0:09:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有个想让你们营救的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.82,0:09:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是个大灾难病毒患者 已经开始肿瘤化了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.37,0:09:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你别急啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.78,0:09:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先联系四分仪先生吧 我这边不能下指示…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.95,0:09:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在就去Point Yellow 1
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.66,0:09:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦一小时后去接应
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.21,0:09:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,集 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.71,0:09:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我并没有原谅你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.34,0:09:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.22,0:09:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,润是无辜的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.32,0:10:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好看着吧 马上就要用它了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.16,0:10:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.16,0:10:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经不是这首歌了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.59,0:10:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 润
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.88,0:10:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍微忍耐下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.01,0:10:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终于出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.06,0:10:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉基因准备如何了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.14,0:10:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经确认正常工作 但为什么要用它…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.23,0:10:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想认识下恋人不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.79,0:10:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请动手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.08,0:11:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anti-bodies？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.33,0:11:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这么快就被发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.92,0:11:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.00,0:11:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事已至此 快行动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.01,0:11:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恐怖袭击？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.47,0:11:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会又是葬仪社吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.93,0:11:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.89,0:11:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用那东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.81,0:11:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.44,0:11:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这肯定是个陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.57,0:11:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在最要紧的是找出逃跑路线 引出敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.57,0:11:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,按你那外行做法 会死人的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.03,0:11:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.16,0:11:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有Void
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.08,0:11:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是能将人心作为武器提取出来的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.17,0:11:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连End Rave都可以干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.59,0:11:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要让我信这话？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.09,0:11:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外面的那群人是你叫来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.26,0:11:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这个伪善者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.72,0:11:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴 叛徒！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.77,0:11:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,集
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.48,0:12:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会像你那样做叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.15,0:12:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会抛弃伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.15,0:12:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会按照约定把润带出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.15,0:12:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你乖乖让我使用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.17,0:12:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,润
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.17,0:12:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要担心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.80,0:12:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你哥哥他没事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.55,0:12:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.18,0:12:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不对？ 什么不对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.98,0:12:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.90,0:12:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无面男
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.49,0:12:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,润 我马上就回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.61,0:12:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逃吧 逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.41,0:12:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但今天可是特别的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.21,0:13:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它会追着那道光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.80,0:13:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挺厉害嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.14,0:13:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就连射如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.78,0:13:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,润
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.91,0:13:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,润！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.79,0:13:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘘界 怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.54,0:13:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也没想到 但这样也挺有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.26,0:13:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那东西和大灾难病毒的肿瘤有相同的反应
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.06,0:14:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.07,0:14:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,转移了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.45,0:14:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.75,0:14:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.72,0:14:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,润
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.22,0:14:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,润 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.47,0:14:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,润！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.02,0:14:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这下怎么跟谷寻交待
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.61,0:15:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大灾难病毒让机器产生了染色体共鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.87,0:15:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么说在那里的应该是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.04,0:15:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重启机器 全部重新连接！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.50,0:15:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.59,0:15:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.05,0:15:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.52,0:15:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘘界少佐 很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.69,0:15:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请撤离
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.57,0:15:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暂时撤退 作战中止
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.99,0:15:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.66,0:15:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.88,0:15:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.49,0:16:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…六本木？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.99,0:16:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lost Christmas发生之前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.62,0:16:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.58,0:16:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是…润？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.75,0:16:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终于能跟你说上话了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.05,0:16:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.13,0:16:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特别的礼物哦 今天是你生日
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.93,0:16:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2029年12月24日
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.69,0:16:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是我最幸福的时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.94,0:17:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再过不久Lost Christmas就要发生了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.74,0:17:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想只带上这份幸福的回忆…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.08,0:17:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后上路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.29,0:17:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,集先生 请用那个Void了结我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.21,0:17:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥的Void是斩断生命的Void
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.38,0:17:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了葬送我的Void
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.02,0:17:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么…可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.94,0:17:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剥夺我自由的结晶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.69,0:17:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,却让我拥有了可以看到Void的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.78,0:17:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的眼睛看到了不同平常的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.58,0:17:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天吃披萨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.45,0:17:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.00,0:17:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢的加了番茄的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.12,0:17:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥帮你订了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.88,0:18:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,碍事 你太碍事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.26,0:18:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不止一次地看到了善良之人邪恶的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.77,0:18:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朋友 阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.60,0:18:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,医疗中心的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.23,0:18:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许集先生你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.36,0:18:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要活下去 这种悲伤就会不断席卷我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.29,0:18:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连哥哥都会变得讨厌起来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.87,0:18:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要喜欢着最喜欢我的哥哥上路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.00,0:18:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.14,0:18:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lost Christmas
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.72,0:18:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 好怕 好怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.02,0:18:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 哥哥跟你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.73,0:19:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永远 永远跟你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.07,0:19:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 这样下去我会杀了哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.70,0:19:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 我是你的累赘？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.99,0:19:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我毁了哥哥的人生？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.87,0:19:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你讨厌我？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.58,0:19:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我其实对哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.30,0:19:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.43,0:19:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜欢哥哥了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.30,0:20:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人生不如意十之八九啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.41,0:20:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.24,0:20:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了 润
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.95,0:20:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,润呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.12,0:20:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.04,0:20:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.13,0:20:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.22,0:21:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,集
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.94,0:21:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.99,0:21:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,集
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.70,0:21:26.75,ed_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}もうあなたから愛されることも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.70,0:21:26.75,ed_sc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}已经不再被你爱护着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.37,0:21:33.42,ed_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}必要とされることもない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.37,0:21:33.42,ed_sc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}也不再被你所需要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.71,0:21:40.06,ed_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}そして私は　こうして一人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.71,0:21:40.06,ed_sc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}我就这样 独自一人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.70,0:21:42.50,ed_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}落ちて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.70,0:21:42.50,ed_sc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}坠落
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.96,0:21:50.03,ed_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}あの時あなたはなんて言ったの
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.96,0:21:50.03,ed_sc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}那时的你说了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.65,0:21:56.72,ed_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}届かない言葉は宙を舞う
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.65,0:21:56.72,ed_sc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}无法传达的言语早已飘逝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.14,0:22:03.39,ed_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}分かってるのに　今日もしてしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.14,0:22:03.39,ed_sc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}虽然心里明白  却又一如从前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.95,0:22:10.03,ed_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}叶わぬ 願いことを
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.95,0:22:10.03,ed_sc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}许下那  无法实现的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.14,0:22:16.74,ed_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}はなさないで　ぎゅっと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.14,0:22:16.74,ed_sc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}请不要放手 紧紧地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.31,0:22:20.12,ed_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}手を握ってて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.31,0:22:20.12,ed_sc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}握住我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.69,0:22:26.96,ed_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}あなたと二人つづくと言って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.69,0:22:26.96,ed_sc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}说好了两人将携手同行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.21,0:22:35.95,ed_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}繋いだ　その手は暖かくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.21,0:22:35.95,ed_sc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}牵着我的那双手是如此温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.96,0:22:44.07,ed_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}優しかった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.96,0:22:44.07,ed_sc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}如此柔和


